# Calendar ‚Äî Visual Specification

## Architecture

All visual styling lives in `packages/css/src/calendar.css` using `@apply` for structural utilities and raw CSS for transitions, animations, and theme overrides.

---

## Class Inventory

### Wrapper & Trigger (dropdown mode)
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-wrapper` | Dropdown wrapper ‚Äî `relative inline-block` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger` | Trigger button ‚Äî `flex items-center justify-between w-full cursor-pointer` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger-open` | Active state ‚Äî primary border + ring |
| `.acko-cal-trigger-placeholder` | Placeholder ‚Äî `color: var(--color-text-muted)` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger-icon` | Calendar icon ‚Äî `flex items-center`, muted color |

### Panel
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-panel` | Calendar container ‚Äî 340px wide, card bg, `--radius-3xl`, `--shadow-md`, `--space-4` padding |
| `.acko-cal-panel-dropdown` | Dropdown positioning ‚Äî `absolute left-0`, z-index, enter animation |

### Header
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-header` | Header row ‚Äî `flex items-center justify-between` |
| `.acko-cal-header-label` | Month/Year label ‚Äî clickable, drills into month ‚Üí year picker |
| `.acko-cal-nav-btn` | Prev/Next nav ‚Äî `--scale-36` square, transparent bg, hover bg |

### Day Grid
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-weekdays` | 7-column grid for weekday headers |
| `.acko-cal-weekday` | Single weekday header ‚Äî uppercase, muted, label-sm |
| `.acko-cal-days` | 7-column grid for day buttons (6 rows √ó 7 = 42 cells) |
| `.acko-cal-day` | Day button ‚Äî `--scale-40` tall, full-radius, `--font-body-sm-size`, tabular-nums |

### Day States
| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-today` | Today ‚Äî `color: var(--color-cal-today-text); font-weight: 700` |
| `.acko-cal-selected` | Selected single ‚Äî `bg: var(--color-cal-selected-bg); color: var(--color-cal-selected-text)` |
| `.acko-cal-range-start` | Range start ‚Äî half-pill left (full-radius left, 0 right) |
| `.acko-cal-range-end` | Range end ‚Äî half-pill right (0 left, full-radius right) |
| `.acko-cal-range-middle` | Range between ‚Äî `bg: var(--color-cal-range-bg); border-radius: 0` |
| `.acko-cal-outside` | Dates outside current month ‚Äî `color: var(--color-text-disabled)` |
| `.acko-cal-day-disabled` | Disabled ‚Äî `color: var(--color-text-muted); cursor-not-allowed` |

### Month/Year Picker
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-picker-grid` | 3-column grid for month or year buttons |
| `.acko-cal-picker-cell` | Picker button ‚Äî `--scale-48` tall, pill radius, `--font-body-sm-size`, 500 weight |
| `.acko-cal-picker-cell-selected` | Active pick ‚Äî selected bg + text, 700 weight |
| `.acko-cal-picker-cell-current` | Current month/year ‚Äî today text color, 700 weight |

