## Tokens Used

| Token | Usage |
|---|---|
| `--color-card-bg` | Panel background |
| `--color-card-border` | Panel border |
| `--color-surface` | Trigger background |
| `--color-surface-raised` | Dark mode trigger bg |
| `--color-border` | Trigger border, dark panel border |
| `--color-primary` | Open/focus border and ring |
| `--color-primary-ring` | Focus-visible ring on nav/header |
| `--color-text-strong` | Day text, header label, picker cell text |
| `--color-text-muted` | Weekday headers, placeholder, disabled days, trigger icon |
| `--color-text-disabled` | Outside-month days |
| `--color-cal-today-text` | Today highlight text |
| `--color-cal-selected-bg` | Selected day background |
| `--color-cal-selected-text` | Selected day text |
| `--color-cal-range-bg` | Range middle band background |
| `--color-cal-range-text` | Range middle band text |
| `--color-cal-cell-hover-bg` | Day/month/year cell hover, header label hover |
| `--shadow-md` | Panel box shadow |
| `--z-dropdown` | Dropdown panel z-index |
| `--radius-full` | Day cells, trigger, picker cells |
| `--radius-3xl` | Panel corner radius |
| `--radius-lg` | Nav button, header label corners |
| `--ease-out-cubic` | Enter animation easing |

---

## Dark Theme Overrides

- Trigger: `var(--color-surface-raised)` bg, `var(--color-border)` border
- Panel: `var(--color-surface-raised)` bg, `var(--color-border)` border

## Elevated Theme Overrides

- Trigger: Glass background with gradient border, backdrop blur, glow
- Open/focus: `var(--elevated-focus-ring)` shadow
- Panel: Glass background, gradient border, 18px blur
